{
  "stem": "18307.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 261.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were actually walking all over bodies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wintertime, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Wintertime.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think it was-- I think it was-- I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think it was March of '44.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we got to Rowne.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was one of the bigger towns near us that-- and I don't know how, but we found a few other Jews, survivors.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Rowne was a big, beautiful, very Jewish city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were all gone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were just a few.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my mother found her brother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My mother walked everywhere, went in one of the houses, and she her brother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He had lost a wife and six children, but he survived.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was it, the war was over.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We didn't go back to my hometown because they bombed my house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My house which was good was flat, so we went to Dubno, where my grandmother and my cousins and my aunts lived.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And naturally, nobody was there-- nobody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] --we just knew.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somebody I guess must have told us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then again, when we lived in Dubno, I wanted to go see for myself.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I went on a truck, on a Russian truck that went to Mlynow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I hitchhiked and went to Mlynow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I never told this to even my parents, but I went to the cemetery and I wanted to see if my brother's, what do you call them, [NON-ENGLISH] was there, you know his marker was there because they knocked-- the Germans knocked down so many of them.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it was there because it was a slab.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was a flat slab.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my-- I never told my parents this.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And from the cemetery, I went into town and actually, the house was gone and it was horrible-- was horrible.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
